336
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:22,400
"The modest, virtuous young lady is a fine match to the gentleman."

337
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:26,400
Miss Yuhan, I am Second Young Master Mei. I have long heard of you.

338
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:30,800
Now that I have met you, you are indeed extraordinary, with the looks of a goddess.

339
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:32,200
Second Young Master Mei, you flatter me.

340
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:36,200
I am saying the truth. When I first saw you, Miss Yuhan,

341
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:40,400
I felt an inexplicable familiarity toward you like I've seen you somewhere before.

342
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:43,200
Do you believe in fate?

343
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,900
That's great!

344
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,800
I also believe in fate.

345
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:51,600
Maybe we met in our previous lives.

346
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:53,400
Shiyuan...

347
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:56,900
