I am so used to drinking the soup you make, this is tasteless.

351
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:25,130
Older Sister, Third Young Master eyes are inconvenient right now,

352
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:27,600
it must be hard on you to take care of him.

353
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:31,200
There are some things... he won't let me do though.

354
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:33,600
Is it because you can't do them?

355
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:36,000
Is it because I don't want the princess to have grievances.

356
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:39,600
Nowadays, the Ninth Prince Manor is no longer as it was before.

357
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:42,600
To be able to marry such a good husband, what kind of grievances could she have?

358
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:45,200
Yuhan, do not speak such nonsense.

359
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:46,800
As an official's daughter,

360
00:24:46,800 --> 00:24:50,200
